Shortcuts:
<F2>  toggle this HELP message
<F3>  toggle between PASTE and NOPASTE mode
<F4>  toggle between TABS and SPACES
<F5>  turns OFF highlighting after SEARCHing
<F7>  DELETE all trailing white characters
<F8>  REPLACE all tab characters by spaces
<F9>  toggle NERDtree
<F11> Start Markdown Preview
<F12> Stop Markdown Preview
